(23, 'Gizmodo.com', 'Lauren Leffer', '\'The Dumpster Fire Is Out:\' Attorneys for Bankrupt FTX Consider Restarting Exchange', 'While SBF and other former FTX execs face criminal fraud charges, the company\'s attorney says they\'ve recovered $7.3 billion in assets.', 'https://gizmodo.com/ftx-sam-bankman-fried-crypto-sbf-1850331812', 'https://i.kinja-img.com/gawker-media/image/upload/c_fill,f_auto,fl_progressive,g_center,h_675,pg_1,q_80,w_1200/110fad4ab8a698a4be70f1d1464dafbe.jpg', '2023-04-13 14:45:00', 'You know that classic zombie movie scene where the everyone thinks the monster is dead, but then suddenly its not?\r\nFTX, the bankrupt crypto exchange that imploded last year, has recouped over $7.3 b… [+2371 chars]', ''),
